title: Pink Floyd covers, female vocals, dub and chill out FLAC
description: The albums of PF cover with diverse interpretations from dub to female vocals. The most interesting one to me is the female vocal covers that have mimimalistic production and easily stand up to repeated listening. The dub version of DSoTM is beat-for-beat to the millisecond the same as the original material, and hence is an equally good backdrop to The Wizard of Oz. The chill out album is just that
